// Interleaving causes a lost update:
T1 reads balance (1000)
T2 reads balance (1000)
T1 writes 1100
T2 writes 1100   ← should be 1200! one deposit lost
// Fix: protect the update in a critical section.

// Counting semaphore guarding a critical section
wait(S):   while S <= 0: wait();  S = S - 1
signal(S): S = S + 1

